A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Opioid Restitution Fund – Interactive Dashboard
3 FOR the purpose of requiring the Maryland Office of Overdose Response, in collaboration
4 with the Maryland Department of Health, to develop and maintain an interactive
5 dashboard on Opioid Restitution Fund spending to share prescription opioid–related
6 settlement information with the public; requiring counties and municipalities
7 receiving settlement funding to provide certain information to the Department to
8 include on the dashboard in a certain manner; requiring that the dashboard be
9 developed and maintained using funds from the Opioid Restitution Fund
10 appropriated through the State budget; and generally relating to an interactive
11 dashboard on Opioid Restitution Fund spending.
12 BY adding to
13 Article – Health – General
14 Section 7.5–1001 to be under the new subtitle “Subtitle 10. Opioid Restitution
15 Settlement Funding Interactive Dashboard”
